<blockquote>Updated on October 30th 2015 – Latest Version 1.4.1</blockquote>
<h2>Set your Blog or Magazine to Eleven with Master</h2>
<a rel="nofollow"  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2C9npQ277fo"><img src="http://co.de125.com/12QhJ+" alt="" /></a>

<p><strong>Master</strong> for <strong>WordPress</strong> stands out from the crowd not only with its elegant and professional design, but in how simple it is to set up and create the perfect website for your Magazine or Blog.</p>
<p>The ease of installation is convenience at its best, you are one-way click from having the demo you saw on your new website*.</p>
<br/>
<p>Why not take a quick tour now?</p>
<a rel="nofollow"  href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2C9npQ277fo"><img src="http://co.de125.com/1hLrg+" alt="" /></a>

<h3>Save with Bundled Extras</h3>
<p>Save over $40 with our <a rel="nofollow"  href="http://codecanyon.net/item/awesome-builder-drag-drop-page-builder/6639589" >Awesome Page</a> Builder Plugin, fully integrated into your theme, giving you the power to create almost any kind of page layout you can imagine - save $28!</p>
<p>Alongside this, you also get <a rel="nofollow"  href="http://codecanyon.net/item/arqam-retina-responsive-wordpress-social-counter-plugin/5085289" >Arqam</a> the powerful responsive 'Social Counter' plugin that rocks your status for absolutely nothing - save $16!</p>
<p>Everything you can think of for a premium features theme comes standard with Master, Predefined layouts, Mega Menu, Layouts, Shortcodes and email subs powered by MailChimp to keep those readers engaged.</p>

<h3>Preview 10 Predefined Homepage Demos</h3>
<p>10 totally smoking hot, full website demos ready for your content. Check em out below!</p>
<a rel="nofollow"  href="http://master.code125.com/"><img src="http://files.code125.com/master/features/demos.jpg" alt="" /></a>

<h3>5 Blog Layouts</h3>
<p>Power up with 5 different distinct Blog layouts, complete with one-click demo content ready to customise. Check out how easy it is with this 30 second video!</p>

<h3>Mega Menu</h3>
<p>You’ll never run out of menu capability with our built in Mega Menu! Define your menu structure with the all too easy Drag and Drop widget editor, Publish your choice of location and the hard work is done.</p>

<h3>3 Slider Options</h3>
<p>Choose from 3 Powerful Sliders to display your pixel-perfect retina-ready photography in full glory.</p>

<h3>40+ Powerful Shortcodes</h3>
<p>With over 40 powerful shortcodes included there isn’t a layout you can’t imagine. Shortcodes enable designers to quickly create pages filled with interactive content, very quickly without any coding.  Bazinga!</p>

<h3>5 Categories Layouts</h3>
<p>Build a Taxonomy using up to 5 Categories and make your content searchable as well as functional.</p>

<h3>1 Click install demo content. Start your new website on the right foot</h3>
<p>One of the most powerful features is our one-click installation. Full demo content on one-click right after  activation of the theme. Up and running in no time!</p>

<h3>Documentation</h3>
<p>Complete Online Documentation with screenshots to help you through the installation and customization process, and of course our Video Tutorials are there to quickly run you through the process.</p>

